short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension is compatible with Cisco product UIs and facilitates the establishment of a Cisco CX Point of Presence.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Cisco Support Assistant (CSA) Extension aims to bring Cisco Support closer to the Cisco products and extend Cisco Technical Assistance Center (TAC) insights and expertise directly inside the Cisco product portals to create a frictionless self-support experience for our customers. Learn more at https://cs.co/extension.
